${GREEN}‚úÖ Where is the root disconnect between current and desired states?${NC}
${GREEN}‚úÖ What are ALL system components and their boundaries?${NC}

${YELLOW}Phase 2: Evidence-Driven Verification${NC}
${GREEN}‚úÖ Test EVERY assumption with concrete evidence${NC}
${GREEN}‚úÖ Build mental model ONLY from verified facts${NC}
${GREEN}‚úÖ Document observations methodically${NC}
${GREEN}‚úÖ No beliefs accepted without verification${NC}

${YELLOW}Phase 3: Minimal Viable Intervention${NC}
${GREEN}‚úÖ Identify the simplest change that achieves the outcome${NC}
${GREEN}‚úÖ Deliver complete working solution with verification${NC}
${GREEN}‚úÖ Confirm outcomes achieved through testing${NC}

${PURPLE}Ready to present this analysis to your AI assistant.${NC}

EOF
}

